42:43.852 --> 42:45.104
<i>I'm coming for you, Manny.</i>

42:46.605 --> 42:48.148
This conversation's over.

42:49.024 --> 42:51.777
Hey, Siri, send a text
to Samantha Browne.

42:52.945 --> 42:54.280
<i>What do you want to say?</i>

42:54.738 --> 42:58.742
Meet me in Washington Square Park
as soon as you can. Urgent.

42:58.742 --> 43:01.328
<i>If you work with Manny Broward,
you can leave right now.</i>

43:02.162 --> 43:03.998
I don't care the consequences.

43:06.375 --> 43:07.585
If it makes any difference,

43:07.585 --> 43:09.920
I may hate Manny Broward
more than you do.

43:12.589 --> 43:14.508
