How about that?

43:19.888 --> 43:20.806
So...

43:22.433 --> 43:23.392
what do you need?

43:25.352 --> 43:27.146
I just wanted to ask about

43:27.980 --> 43:31.900
the ties between you, Manny Broward,

43:31.900 --> 43:35.195
the Brownes, your brother,
and Guyana.

43:36.780 --> 43:39.491
- Guyana?
- Why are you bringing up Guyana?

43:39.491 --> 43:40.951
- What is--
- No, no, no.

43:41.827 --> 43:42.995
The kidnapping.

43:43.829 --> 43:45.748
It had something to do with Guyana.

43:46.999 --> 43:49.793
- Right?
- I think so, yeah. Why?

43:51.295 --> 43:53.005
I made a very bad mistake.

43:54.048 --> 43:55.341
And I paid the price.

43:56.508 --> 44:00.304
The NYPD has the full
internal affairs report,

44:01.221 --> 44:03.557
and I'm sure you can look it up
if you wanted to.

44:03.557 --> 44:06.727
- The charges were dropped.
- Listen, she knows, Cindy.

44:07.519 --> 44:09.605
She knows what really happened.
She's a pro.

44:10.439 --> 44:11.440
Aren't you?

44:12.775 --> 44:14.943
- You know how it's done.
- Your foot.

44:17.946 --> 44:18.864
Yeah.

44:20.032 --> 44:24.995
So how full is this "full" report?

44:25.454 --> 44:28.374
- Is Manny Broward mentioned in it?
- What do you think?

44:30.584 --> 44:33.045
I think he figured out a way
to keep himself clean.

44:35.047 --> 44:37.257
But you think Manny was involved,

44:37.257 --> 44:40.928
but somehow Jeffrey was the one
who turned you in.

44:41.804 --> 44:42.971
Yeah. I know.

44:44.181 --> 44:45.140
You have proof?

44:50.396 --> 44:51.647
You're holding proof.

44:54.274 --> 44:56.568
But you're not gonna tell me
no matter how mad you get

44:56.568 --> 44:58.362
because you don't want to be
like your brother.

44:58.362 --> 45:00.364
Gene has already been
through hell with this, it--

45:00.364 --> 45:02.908
Oh, I... I'm not trying
to take him back to that.

45:02.908 --> 45:04.201
Don't worry.

45:04.201 --> 45:07.621
I'm just trying to figure out
who organized this debacle

45:07.621 --> 45:10.165
in the park the other night and why?

45:13.710 --> 45:14.670
But...

45:15.129 --> 45:19.341
I see that I'm gonna get
no further here, so...

45:22.636 --> 45:26.432
One final question
that won't leave the room.

45:27.724 --> 45:32.146
Do you have anything at all
that might implicate

45:32.730 --> 45:35.482
others that are outside
of this immediate circle?

45:36.400 --> 45:37.776
Someone in another city?

45:38.819 --> 45:40.028
Maybe a bank name?

45:41.739 --> 45:42.656
Why?

45:42.990 --> 45:45.159
Just trying to help
a colleague at the bureau.

45:45.784 --> 45:49.788
But I see you're not gonna say anything
because you're trying to protect someone.

45:52.458 --> 45:55.043
I wish I had someone like you
watching out for me.

45:57.337 --> 45:58.297
Thank you.

46:01.341 --> 46:02.259
Detective.

46:09.266 --> 46:10.184
You're welcome.

46:11.643 --> 46:14.646
<i>Hey, Xav. It's me.</i>

46:16.231 --> 46:17.608
<i>I'm sorry I haven't called.</i>

46:18.901 --> 46:22.070
<i>We weren't sure if it was safe
and we didn't want to get you in trouble.</i>

46:24.031 --> 46:24.948
<i>But mostly,</i>

46:25.908 --> 46:27.826
<i>I feel bad because I lied to you.</i>

46:30.037 --> 46:31.121
<i>We're okay.</i>

46:45.844 --> 46:48.055
-<i>Hello?</i>
- Yo, Shakeela.

46:48.847 --> 46:50.307
- It's me.
-<i>I know it's you.</i>

46:50.307 --> 46:51.642
<i>Where have you been?</i>

46:51.642 --> 46:54.228
Look, I know. I'm sorry.
I should've called. I just...

46:55.103 --> 46:56.688
I just been busy with work, you know.

46:57.231 --> 47:00.359
<i>Xavier, I was really worried
something might have happened to you.</i>

47:00.359 --> 47:02.444
And I know. I make it up to you.

47:02.444 --> 47:05.656
-<i>Okay, I'm listening.</i>
- Are you still at school?

47:05.656 --> 47:07.241
<i>No, we're done for today.</i>

47:08.283 --> 47:09.284
All right, good.

47:10.244 --> 47:12.079
'Cause you'll never guess where I'm at.

47:12.829 --> 47:15.082
Accessory after the fact, Sam.

47:15.541 --> 47:18.627
That's what you're facing
if you talk to Mel Harmony

47:18.627 --> 47:21.004
or anyone. I mean, it...

47:22.256 --> 47:24.216
There's no statute of limitations.

47:26.677 --> 47:29.346
The first round of funding
that your Uncle Gene

47:29.346 --> 47:30.973
knowingly brought you in on,

47:32.057 --> 47:36.103
those were all bribes. Paying off
one corrupt politician after another.

47:38.188 --> 47:42.025
That is what you did.
And that's what I protected you from.

47:43.485 --> 47:47.114
- By having me bury evidence.
- Yes. That's true. Yeah.

47:48.907 --> 47:52.035
Which I assume is also why you
don't want me to say anything

47:52.035 --> 47:53.829
because you could go down as well?

47:53.829 --> 47:56.707
You know what?
I've worked for 30 years, Sam,

47:56.707 --> 48:00.127
on a public servant's salary, all right?

48:00.127 --> 48:03.338
I have a NYPD pension,

48:03.714 --> 48:05.841
a USPIS one.

48:06.425 --> 48:10.971
- That goes, all that goes, if you...
- What? Tell the truth?

48:11.471 --> 48:14.433
Tell a different truth
than you did 20 years ago.

48:21.732 --> 48:23.984
You got my uncle's job, didn't you?

48:24.735 --> 48:29.156
- When I did what I did.
- Buried evidence.

48:29.156 --> 48:31.575
- No, please just answer my question.
- Yeah, yeah. Yeah.

48:31.575 --> 48:34.369
I saw an opportunity
for advancement and I took it.

48:35.037 --> 48:38.707
But... I didn't take down
an innocent man.

48:39.875 --> 48:42.085
I took down a guilty man, and...

48:44.588 --> 48:45.589
I saved you.

48:47.299 --> 48:48.425
And your dad.

48:50.302 --> 48:53.305
They have nothing
unless you give it to them.

48:54.640 --> 48:56.767
Well, I don't have anything to give them.

48:57.100 --> 48:59.978
It was all destroyed 20 years ago,
as instructed.

49:01.730 --> 49:02.981
Well, that's perfect then.

49:04.316 --> 49:06.610
Then you don't have to do anything.

49:08.278 --> 49:09.905
All you have to do is nothing.

49:10.656 --> 49:13.408
All right? And then everything
goes back to normal.

49:27.923 --> 49:30.842
We believe it's Natalia, my masseuse.

49:30.842 --> 49:33.845
She been working her own obeah
through her hands.

49:34.513 --> 49:36.890
It's the only thing making sense.

49:37.224 --> 49:39.976
The only reason the circle
could've been broken.

49:41.478 --> 49:43.647
Okay. This can't be about the curse.

49:43.647 --> 49:45.982
You seen the troubles we've been having?

49:46.316 --> 49:48.276
All the troubles are not about the curse

49:48.276 --> 49:50.987
put on your family years ago
for whatever reason.

49:51.697 --> 49:55.450
They're about choices
your husband made, you made,

49:56.326 --> 49:57.327
we all made.

49:57.869 --> 50:01.540
Mr. Willoughby is aware
of the break in the circle,

50:02.249 --> 50:04.501
and has taken reparative measures.

50:05.419 --> 50:08.547
Soon, all will be good.

50:09.131 --> 50:11.007
I be dipping a sinking ship, raas.

50:12.843 --> 50:14.094
Any news from Xavier?

50:14.886 --> 50:18.932
- Girlfriend's moving. Len following her.
- Again with the girlfriend.

50:20.892 --> 50:22.811
To be 19. Go bring he here.

50:25.063 --> 50:27.399
Come on, come on. All right.

50:28.191 --> 50:29.443
One second.

50:30.110 --> 50:32.988
All right, Xavier. It's your time.
You got this one.

50:37.617 --> 50:38.618
Okay.

50:41.872 --> 50:43.206
- You all right?
- Hi.

50:45.333 --> 50:47.919
- It's good to see you.
- Wow.

50:48.295 --> 50:51.131
- This... this is nice.
- Right?

50:52.382 --> 50:55.010
- Welcome to the high life.
- How did you afford this?

50:56.470 --> 50:57.846
It's just a work thing, you know.

50:59.347 --> 51:00.599
They pay for it all.

51:01.808 --> 51:03.602
- Are you hungry?
- Always.

51:03.602 --> 51:05.020
All right, then.

51:06.104 --> 51:08.648
- You can pick anything you want.
- Okay.

51:10.567 --> 51:12.736
...and blue cheese. That's my go-to.

51:12.736 --> 51:15.906
- For real?
- Okay, I'm gonna have to try that.

51:20.869 --> 51:22.454
Hey, Shakeela, maybe you should go wait

51:22.454 --> 51:23.705
- in the bedroom.
- Why?

51:23.705 --> 51:25.874
Can you just go and wait
in the bedroom, please?

51:30.670 --> 51:32.422
It's just some work stuff, all right?

51:37.636 --> 51:39.971
I soon come. I coming back just now.

51:42.390 --> 51:45.018
- Xavier, open up.
- This ain't...

51:47.395 --> 51:48.438
Okay.

51:50.565 --> 51:51.858
This ain't what you think.

51:53.026 --> 51:56.238
Hey, what the fuck?
Damn, just relax, my man.

51:56.571 --> 51:58.114
Wait. Wait. No, man.

51:58.114 --> 52:00.408
This ain't what you think.
This ain't what you think, man!

52:01.076 --> 52:02.369
I promise this ain't what you think.

52:02.869 --> 52:06.748
Okay, let me be more accurate
on your assessment of what I do think.

52:07.833 --> 52:10.001
I think you're a piece of shit liar.

52:11.628 --> 52:12.879
And maybe even worse.

52:13.839 --> 52:14.631
Paul!

52:15.465 --> 52:16.675
- Oh, shit.
- Okay.

52:17.259 --> 52:19.427
Now one of two things are true.

52:19.427 --> 52:22.013
Either you're the snitch,
not Louis and Natalia,

52:22.347 --> 52:25.016
or you got caught and now you're singing.

52:25.350 --> 52:26.351
Either way...

52:28.270 --> 52:30.981
- we, you, fucked.
- I can explain.

52:31.773 --> 52:34.776
- Ankle bracelet explains it all.
- I can explain to Garmen.

52:35.652 --> 52:38.405
He send you here to take me to him, right?

52:38.405 --> 52:40.490
I should fucking kill you myself,
you fucking traitor.

52:40.490 --> 52:42.742
No, if Garmen wanted me dead,
I'll be dead.

52:43.243 --> 52:45.453
Which means he sent you here
to take me to him,

52:45.453 --> 52:47.122
